该党有两个军事组织：在农村是人民解放军（{{lang|tr|Halk Kurtuluş Ordusu}}），在城市是人民游击力量（{{lang|tr|Partizan Halk Güçleri}}）。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E-SZ4FQOE7A|title=MAOİST KOMÜNİST PARTİSİ-MKP/HKO|date=13 February 2007|work=YouTube|accessdate=7 March 2015|archive-date=2016-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160428214121/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E-SZ4FQOE7A|dead-url=no}}</ref>

青年组织是毛主义青年联盟（{{lang|tr|Maoist Gençlik Birliği}}）。妇女组织是毛主义妇女联盟（{{lang|tr|Maoist Kadınlar Birliği}}）。

该党出版两个期刊：《革命民主》（{{lang|tr|Devrimci Demokrasi}}）和《阶级理论》（{{lang|tr|Sınıf Teorisi}}）。<ref name="Leftist Parties of Turkey">{{cite web|url=http://www.broadleft.org/tr.htm|title=Leftist Parties of Turkey|work=broadleft.org|accessdate=6 October 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130730090448/http://www.broadleft.org/tr.htm|archive-date=2013-07-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

民主权利联盟（{{lang|tr|Demokratik Haklar Federasyonu}}）是与该党有关的独立群众组织。

